{"tid":2299693,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［急］今朝有冇人執到單邊airpod pro右邊耳機","createTime":"2020-11-25T03:42:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-25T06:47:57.000Z","uid":17351,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"090a9e15da750ae79de76c960115d0cd41bda7a9","tid":2299693,"uid":17351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T03:42:26.000Z","msg":"幫人問<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇人今朝大約<span class=\"xx-large\">7點50分左右搭西鐵線由錦上路去緊荃灣西</span>嘅嗰班車，執到隻airpod pro嘅<span class=\"xx-large\">右邊</span>耳機<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢岩岩買左冇耐嫁炸..！唔見左一邊真係想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢話跌左嗰下即刻就搵，但搵左陣都見唔到地下有，懷疑係唔小心跌左落人地個袋到。希望全能嘅連登仔幫幫手，佢只係想開開心心咁聽歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">好人一生平安</span>，如果真係搵到，我留telegram聯絡<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔該大家"},{"pid":"9ccb6276cc5730140e32b2d4df6f83d7e7398e4d","tid":2299693,"uid":201299,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T03:42:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0449bd2600e2dbc15d12daa298fa7ca9cec766fd","tid":2299693,"uid":17351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T03:42:58.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"348c958919f752fc9aab44c11ac7ed5d610e5f6d","tid":2299693,"uid":17351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ccb6276cc5730140e32b2d4df6f83d7e7398e4d","tid":2299693,"uid":201299,"like